<item>
            <title>[LU-3280] when lock-&gt;l_lvb_data is freed, LDLM_FL_LVB_READY is not cleared</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3280</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in ldlm_lock_decref_internal() when l_lvb_data is freed to reduce memory consumption, LDLM_FL_LVB_READY is not cleared, so later when the lock is reused lvb is never updated. We hit this case after a restore in HSM.&lt;br/&gt;
Patch will follow&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
