                            <comment id="57932" author="jlevi" created="Wed, 8 May 2013 18:41:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closing ticket as patch landed to master. If more work is needed, please let me know and I&apos;ll reopen.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="57757" author="jay" created="Mon, 6 May 2013 18:57:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, it will affect normal usage of 2.4 because the inode can be purged by kernel but the corresponding layout lock can still exist. We should include this in 2.4.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="57756" author="adilger" created="Mon, 6 May 2013 18:54:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jinshan, can you please take a look at this bug and see whether this will affect normal usage in 2.4.0, or does it only affect HSM?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
